Instructions:

   BCC  Zeros  opcode     ope2      IV
0x|0000|0000|0|0000|0000|0000|0000|00000000
             IV     ope1     dest

r0 0000
r1 0001
r2 0010
...
r15 1111

add r1, r1, 3 r1 = r1 +3
add r1, 3 r1 = r1 +3


 
Structure de donnees:
   - r0..r15   -> registre "utilisateur"
   - PC        -> pointe vers la prochaine instruction
   - Flag      -> a determiner:
      -flag compare ->
         BEQ ope1 = ope2 
         BNE ope1 !=ope2 
         BLE ope1 ≤ ope2 
         BGE ope1 ≥ ope2 
         BL  ope1 < ope2 
         BG  ope1 > ope2 



